#. <section class="sutta" id="sn55.37"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn55.37:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 55"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 55"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.37:0.2"
msgid "4. Puññābhisandavagga"
msgstr "4. Overflowing Merit"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn55.37:0.3"
msgid "37. Mahānāmasutta"
msgstr "37. With Mahānāma"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.395"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.37:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sakkesu viharati kapilavatthusmiṃ nigrodhārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying in the land of the Sakyans, near "
"Kapilavatthu in the Banyan Tree Monastery."

msgctxt "sn55.37:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho mahānāmo sakko yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho mahānāmo "
"sakko bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Mahānāma the Sakyan went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, "
"and said to him:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.37:2.1"
msgid "“Kittāvatā nu kho, bhante, upāsako hotī”ti?"
msgstr "“Sir, how is a lay follower defined?”"

msgctxt "sn55.37:2.2"
msgid ""
"“Yato kho, mahānāma, buddhaṃ saraṇaṃ gato hoti, dhammaṃ saraṇaṃ gato hoti, "
"saṅghaṃ saraṇaṃ gato hoti—"
msgstr ""
"“Mahānāma, when you’ve gone for refuge to the Buddha, the teaching, and the "
"Saṅgha,"

msgctxt "sn55.37:2.3"
msgid "ettāvatā kho, mahānāma, upāsako hotī”ti."
msgstr "you’re considered to be a lay follower.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.37:3.1"
msgid "“Kittāvatā pana, bhante, upāsako sīlasampanno hotī”ti?"
msgstr "“But how is an ethical lay follower defined?”"

msgctxt "sn55.37:3.2"
msgid ""
"“Yato kho, mahānāma, upāsako pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti, adinnādānā "
"paṭivirato hoti, kāmesumicchācārā paṭivirato hoti, musāvādā paṭivirato hoti, "
"surāmerayamajjappamādaṭṭhānā paṭivirato hoti—"
msgstr ""
"“When a lay follower doesn’t kill living creatures, steal, commit sexual "
"misconduct, lie, or consume alcoholic drinks that cause negligence,"

msgctxt "sn55.37:3.3"
msgid "ettāvatā kho, mahānāma, upāsako sīlasampanno hotī”ti."
msgstr "they’re considered to be an ethical lay follower.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.37:4.1"
msgid "“Kittāvatā pana, bhante, upāsako saddhāsampanno hotī”ti?"
msgstr "“But how is a faithful lay follower defined?”"

msgctxt "sn55.37:4.2"
msgid "“Idha, mahānāma, upāsako saddho hoti, saddahati tathāgatassa bodhiṃ—"
msgstr "“It’s when a lay follower has faith in the Realized One’s awakening:"

msgctxt "sn55.37:4.3"
msgid "itipi so bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavāti."
msgstr ""
"‘That Blessed One is perfected, a fully awakened Buddha, accomplished in "
"knowledge and conduct, holy, knower of the world, supreme guide for those "
"who wish to train, teacher of gods and humans, awakened, blessed.’"

msgctxt "sn55.37:4.4"
msgid "Ettāvatā kho, mahānāma, upāsako saddhāsampanno hotī”ti."
msgstr "Then they’re considered to be a faithful lay follower.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.37:5.1"
msgid "“Kittāvatā pana, bhante, upāsako cāgasampanno hotī”ti?"
msgstr "“But how is a generous lay follower defined?”"

msgctxt "sn55.37:5.2"
msgid ""
"“Idha, mahānāma, upāsako vigatamalamaccherena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati "
"muttacāgo payatapāṇi vossaggarato yācayogo dānasaṃvibhāgarato—"
msgstr ""
"“It’s when a lay follower lives at home rid of the stain of stinginess, "
"freely generous, open-handed, loving to let go, committed to charity, loving "
"to give and to share."

msgctxt "sn55.37:5.3"
msgid "ettāvatā kho, mahānāma, upāsako cāgasampanno hotī”ti."
msgstr "Then they’re considered to be a generous lay follower.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.37:6.1"
msgid "“Kittāvatā pana, bhante, upāsako paññāsampanno hotī”ti?"
msgstr "“But how is a wise lay follower defined?”"

msgctxt "sn55.37:6.2"
msgid ""
"“Idha, mahānāma, upāsako paññavā hoti udayatthagāminiyā paññāya samannāgato "
"ariyāya nibbedhikāya sammā dukkhakkhayagāminiyā—"
msgstr ""
"“It’s when a lay follower is wise. They have the wisdom of arising and "
"passing away which is noble, penetrative, and leads to the complete ending "
"of suffering."

msgctxt "sn55.37:6.3"
msgid "ettāvatā kho, mahānāma, upāsako paññāsampanno hotī”ti."
msgstr "Then they’re considered to be a wise lay follower.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.37:6.4"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
